   <title>Version 1.5.1+1</title>
   <pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 17:03:03 +0000</pubDate>
   <description>## Plug Agente 1.5.1

- Application version **1.5.1+1** (`pubspec.yaml`, Windows build, installer).
- Fixes the auto-update flow by falling back to the official appcast feed when `AUTO_UPDATE_FEED_URL` is not explicitly configured.
- Updates GitHub artifact actions to Node 24-compatible versions to remove Node 20 deprecation warnings from CI and release automation.

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cesar-carlos/plug_agente/compare/v1.5.0...v1.5.1</description>
