  </item>
  <item>
   <title>Version 1.5.0+1</title>
   <pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 16:46:54 +0000</pubDate>
   <description>## Plug Agente 1.5.0

- Application version **1.5.0+1** (`pubspec.yaml`, Windows build, installer).
- Includes hardened hub reconnect and session recovery, SQL investigation feed and ODBC batch context improvements, and client token flow updates already merged to `main`.
- Ships the Windows installer with the official auto-update feed embedded.

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cesar-carlos/plug_agente/compare/v1.4.0...v1.5.0</description>
