  <item>
   <title>Version 1.4.0+1</title>
   <pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 20:36:03 +0000</pubDate>
   <description>## Plug Agente 1.4.0

- Application version **1.4.0+1** (\pubspec.yaml\, Windows build, installer).
- Includes **JSON-RPC profile 2.9** with \^Ggent.getHealth\, SQL queue metrics, and related contract updates from prior commits on \main\.

Build the Windows installer after \lutter build windows --release\ using Inno Setup with \installer/setup.iss\ (output: \installer/dist/PlugAgente-Setup-1.4.0.exe\).</description>
